消費呢場運動?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30ZC4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30ZC4p.png&h=bda94586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返去玩玩具啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">絲打們要小心,好撚多呢種垃圾狗公借機搵食<br />\n<br />\n特別係呢條死狗公 許家偉!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">會員 #86726你收嗲啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">一開始極力為厹偉護航<br />\n<br />\n其後被網友踢爆 發現佢正正係厹偉本人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9e0yQMF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9e0yQMF.png&h=39c0f641&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係咪屌厭左條女所以持久唔到啊,早洩偉?<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"715d5ffc6fa1f987f6858107f309226151010740","tid":1729852,"uid":297794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9608a9c9c34edae8b2278e7d53fee9b1a022389b","tid":1729852,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"無睇過ming仔，只睇過熊仔頭<br />\n香港人睇youtuber只係睇吃喝玩樂，無啦啦逼晒youtuber落政治水，都幾好笑<br />\n真係俾你睇政治既youtube頻道，睇3分鍾咪又恰眼訓<br />\n講到尾睇娛樂性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"佢係唔出聲好過出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}